<li id="cite_note-NYT2008-2"><b><a href="#cite_ref-NYT2008_2-0" title="">^</a></b> <cite style="font-style:normal" class="news" id="CITEREFJody_Rosen2008">Jody Rosen (March 27, 2008). <a href="http://www.nytimes.com/2008/03/27/arts/27soun.html" class="external text" title="http://www.nytimes.com/2008/03/27/arts/27soun.html" rel="nofollow">"Researchers Play Tune Recorded Before Edison"</a>. <a href="/wiki/New_York_Times" title="New York Times" class="mw-redirect">New York Times</a><span class="printonly">. <a href="http://www.nytimes.com/2008/03/27/arts/27soun.html" class="external free" title="http://www.nytimes.com/2008/03/27/arts/27soun.html" rel="nofollow">http://www.nytimes.com/2008/03/27/arts/27soun.html</a></span>.</cite><span class="Z3988" title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=bookitem&amp;rft.btitle=Researchers+Play+Tune+Recorded+Before+Edison&amp;rft.atitle=&amp;rft.aulast=Jody+Rosen&amp;rft.au=Jody+Rosen&amp;rft.date=March+27%2C+2008&amp;rft.pub=%5B%5BNew+York+Times%5D%5D&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.nytimes.com%2F2008%2F03%2F27%2Farts%2F27soun.html&amp;rfr_id=info:sid/en.wikipedia.org:Sound_recording_and_reproduction"><span style="display: none;">&#160;</span></span></li>
